27:39.720 --> 27:41.880
<font color="#00ff00">Why would he do that?</font>

27:46.040 --> 27:49.518
<font color="#00ffff">I do remember he'd been borrowing</font>
<font color="#00ffff">money left, right and centre.</font>

27:49.520 --> 27:51.918
<font color="#00ffff">Got himself in a right state.</font>

27:51.920 --> 27:54.598
<font color="#00ff00">Did he borrow any money off you?</font>

27:54.600 --> 27:58.038
<font color="#00ffff">I never lend money to friends.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I learned that the hard way.</font>

27:58.040 --> 28:00.518
<font color="#00ff00">What did he want</font>
<font color="#00ff00">with all that money?</font>

28:00.520 --> 28:04.038
<font color="#00ffff">His daughter, I think. It's a</font>
<font color="#00ffff">long time ago. I can't be sure.</font>

28:04.040 --> 28:06.040
<font color="#00ff00">What about his daughter?</font>

28:09.280 --> 28:11.360
<font color="#00ffff">She was sick, poor kid.</font>

28:12.360 --> 28:14.040
<font color="#00ffff">Terminal, it was.</font>

28:15.760 --> 28:19.038
<font color="#00ffff">I think his wife Sue wanted</font>
<font color="#00ffff">some new treatment for her.</font>

28:19.040 --> 28:21.278
<font color="#00ffff">It was going to cost a fortune,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">though.</font>

28:21.280 --> 28:23.640
<font color="#00ffff">I think the poor kid died anyway.</font>

28:28.760 --> 28:30.518
<font color="#00ffff">That body you found.</font>

28:30.520 --> 28:32.238
<font color="#00ffff">Is it Derek?</font>

28:32.240 --> 28:34.400
<font color="#00ff00">I'm afraid it is.</font>

28:39.240 --> 28:40.758
<font color="#ffffff">Guv. </font><font color="#00ff00">Yeah?</font>

28:40.760 --> 28:43.760
<font color="#ffffff">We've got Derek Marshall's wife's</font>
<font color="#ffffff">current address.</font>

28:54.280 --> 28:56.320
<font color="#ffffff">SIREN WAILS</font>

29:09.040 --> 29:10.680
<font color="#ffff00">Mrs Marshall?</font>

29:14.520 --> 29:16.040
<font color="#00ffff">Bugger off!</font>

29:18.520 --> 29:21.040
<font color="#ffff00">Mrs Marshall.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">You've got the wrong house!</font>

29:23.040 --> 29:25.278
<font color="#00ffff">I'm an atheist!</font>

29:25.280 --> 29:28.520
<font color="#ffff00">It's the police.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Can you open the door, please?</font>

29:29.520 --> 29:31.520
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, yeah, here she comes.</font>

29:33.240 --> 29:35.000
<font color="#00ff00">Here's my ID.</font>

29:40.280 --> 29:42.198
<font color="#00ffff">Come back tomorrow.</font>

29:42.200 --> 29:44.038
<font color="#00ffff">I'm not well.</font>

29:44.040 --> 29:45.520
<font color="#00ff00">Mrs Marshall. Sue?</font>

29:47.040 --> 29:50.360
<font color="#00ff00">We have some news about</font>
<font color="#00ff00">your husband Derek.</font>

29:54.040 --> 29:55.838
<font color="#00ff00">OK, let's bring her in.</font>

29:55.840 --> 29:57.280
<font color="#ffff00">Guv.</font>

30:03.760 --> 30:06.278
<font color="#ffff00">Hi. How was it? </font><font color="#00ff00">Yeah, petty grim.</font>

30:06.280 --> 30:08.758
<font color="#00ff00">Smells of damp, threadbare carpet.</font>

30:08.760 --> 30:11.238
<font color="#00ff00">No wonder she didn't want to</font>
<font color="#00ff00">let us in.</font>

30:11.240 --> 30:13.438
<font color="#ffff00">That doesn't make any sense,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">does it?</font>

30:13.440 --> 30:16.518
<font color="#ffff00">She had 365 grand</font>
<font color="#ffff00">from the sale of the house</font>

30:16.520 --> 30:19.278
<font color="#ffff00">and another 200</font>
<font color="#ffff00">from the insurance company.</font>

30:19.280 --> 30:22.518
<font color="#ffff00">Why is she living like that?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Where's all her money gone?</font>

30:22.520 --> 30:25.278
<font color="#00ff00">Well, Derek racked up a lot of debt</font>
<font color="#00ff00">before he died.</font>

30:25.280 --> 30:27.358
<font color="#ffff00">To pay for his daughter's treatment.</font>

30:27.360 --> 30:30.518
<font color="#00ff00">We've got him making a lot of big</font>
<font color="#00ff00">payments to an offshore account</font>

30:30.520 --> 30:33.278
<font color="#00ff00">but the trail's scrambled</font>
<font color="#00ff00">and we can't get a clear picture</font>

30:33.280 --> 30:34.918
<font color="#00ff00">of where that money went.</font>

30:34.920 --> 30:37.358
<font color="#ffff00">I can look at the journey</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of the money, if you like.</font>

30:37.360 --> 30:39.720
<font color="#ffff00">See if I can unscramble it. </font><font color="#00ff00">Good.</font>

30:44.480 --> 30:46.118
<font color="#ffff00">We have your statement here</font>

30:46.120 --> 30:48.760
<font color="#ffff00">from when Derek was reported</font>
<font color="#ffff00">missing in 1999.</font>

30:55.520 --> 30:59.158
<font color="#00ff00">You say he left the house</font>
<font color="#00ff00">with no clothes, no wallet,</font>

30:59.160 --> 31:02.518
<font color="#00ff00">no passport and never came home.</font>

31:02.520 --> 31:04.358
<font color="#00ff00">Why would he do that?</font>

31:04.360 --> 31:05.838
<font color="#00ffff">I don't know.</font>

31:05.840 --> 31:09.278
<font color="#00ff00">Your sister-in-law tells us</font>
<font color="#00ff00">there was some tension in the home.</font>

31:09.280 --> 31:10.758
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, yeah.</font>

31:10.760 --> 31:12.520
<font color="#00ffff">Sounds like Ann.</font>

31:13.520 --> 31:16.240
<font color="#00ffff">Never quite got over Derek</font>
<font color="#00ffff">getting married.</font>

31:17.240 --> 31:21.158
<font color="#00ff00">So you had a good relationship</font>
<font color="#00ff00">with your husband, then?</font>

31:21.160 --> 31:24.158
<font color="#00ffff">Yes, I did.</font>

31:24.160 --> 31:26.958
<font color="#00ffff">Ann took advantage of him</font>
<font color="#00ffff">his whole life.</font>

31:26.960 --> 31:29.278
<font color="#00ffff">Never took responsibility</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for herself.</font>

31:29.280 --> 31:32.360
<font color="#00ffff">Always on the doorstep with her</font>
<font color="#00ffff">hand out, selfish to the core.</font>

31:33.360 --> 31:35.600
<font color="#00ffff">Derek could never say no to her.</font>

31:37.520 --> 31:39.440
<font color="#00ffff">I couldn't understand it.</font>

31:41.760 --> 31:45.880
<font color="#00ffff">It was Ann who pushed him</font>
<font color="#00ffff">over the edge, not me!</font>

31:51.040 --> 31:53.760
<font color="#00ff00">So your husband did take</font>
<font color="#00ff00">his own life, then?</font>

31:56.280 --> 31:58.520
<font color="#00ff00">Did Derek take his own life, Sue?</font>

31:59.520 --> 32:02.040
<font color="#00ff00">Is that why you didn't</font>
<font color="#00ff00">report him missing?</font>

32:08.280 --> 32:11.358
<font color="#00ff00">We've been to the house that</font>
<font color="#00ff00">you and Derek lived in together</font>

32:11.360 --> 32:13.758
<font color="#00ff00">and we found Derek's blood</font>
<font color="#00ff00">in the bathroom.</font>

32:13.760 --> 32:17.558
<font color="#00ff00">Postmortem indicates that he took</font>
<font color="#00ff00">his own life by cutting his wrists.</font>

32:17.560 --> 32:20.958
<font color="#00ff00">But a crude attempt was made</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to cover up that suicide</font>

32:20.960 --> 32:23.840
<font color="#00ff00">by removing his hands.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Did you remove his hands, Sue?</font>

32:30.760 --> 32:33.758
<font color="#00ff00">He had only recently taken out</font>
<font color="#00ff00">a life insurance policy</font>

32:33.760 --> 32:36.278
<font color="#00ff00">so they wouldn't have paid out</font>
<font color="#00ff00">for a suicide,</font>

32:36.280 --> 32:38.360
<font color="#00ff00">and you needed that money, correct?</font>

32:39.520 --> 32:42.478
<font color="#00ff00">Derek had left you with</font>
<font color="#00ff00">a mountain of debt.</font>

32:42.480 --> 32:45.280
<font color="#00ff00">What did you need all that</font>
<font color="#00ff00">money for, Sue?</font>

32:48.760 --> 32:50.600
<font color="#00ff00">Treatment for your daughter?</font>

32:54.000 --> 32:56.080
<font color="#00ff00">Was that your idea?</font>

33:02.040 --> 33:03.520
<font color="#00ffff">No comment.</font>

33:10.280 --> 33:12.520
<font color="#ffff00">Mrs Marshall,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you are under caution...</font>

33:13.520 --> 33:16.040
<font color="#ffff00">..for the unlawful disposal</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of a dead body.</font>

33:19.400 --> 33:21.560
<font color="#00ffff">I'm not going to say anything else.</font>

33:23.760 --> 33:25.200
<font color="#00ff00">Right.</font>

33:29.760 --> 33:32.358
<font color="#ffff00">Can you give me a lift</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to the hospital? It's urgent.</font>

33:32.360 --> 33:34.758
<font color="#ffff00">I can't wait for a taxi.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Yeah, of course. </font><font color="#ffff00">Thanks.</font>

33:34.760 --> 33:37.278
<font color="#ffffff">Anything I can do?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Mum's being aggressive.</font>

33:37.280 --> 33:39.638
<font color="#ffff00">Struck a porter around the face,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">apparently.</font>

33:39.640 --> 33:41.758
<font color="#ffffff">She's just confused.</font>

33:41.760 --> 33:44.040
<font color="#ffff00">Why have they refused to treat her?</font>

33:52.040 --> 33:53.518
<font color="#ffff00">I'm so sorry.</font>

33:53.520 --> 33:55.758
<font color="#ffff00">Was the porter all right? </font><font color="#ffffff">He's fine.</font>

33:55.760 --> 33:59.000
<font color="#ffff00">Hello, Mum.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">What have you been up to, eh?</font>

34:00.000 --> 34:03.118
<font color="#ffff00">You really must be kinder</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to the doctors and nurses.</font>

34:03.120 --> 34:05.518
<font color="#ffffff">It's all been a bit much for her,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">bless her.</font>

34:05.520 --> 34:08.358
<font color="#ffffff">She just wants to be left alone,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">not poked and prodded.</font>

34:08.360 --> 34:11.277
<font color="#ffffff">The doctor prescribed Diazepam</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to calm her down.</font>

34:11.280 --> 34:14.318
<font color="#00ffff">Is that really necessary?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">It was just a little dose.</font>

34:14.320 --> 34:17.757
<font color="#ffffff">She was distressed and we were</font>
<font color="#ffffff">worried that she might hurt herself.</font>

34:17.760 --> 34:19.679
<font color="#ffffff">But now she won't eat.</font>

34:21.040 --> 34:22.600
<font color="#ffff00">Let me try.</font>

34:27.040 --> 34:30.598
<font color="#ffff00">Remember when you used to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">make me chicken noodle soup</font>

34:30.600 --> 34:32.320
<font color="#ffff00">when I was poorly?</font>

34:33.320 --> 34:36.757
<font color="#ffff00">If you can manage</font>
<font color="#ffff00">a couple of spoons,</font>

34:36.760 --> 34:39.678
<font color="#ffff00">I'm sure you'd feel... </font><font color="#00ff00">No!</font>
<font color="#ffff00">..better.</font>

34:39.679 --> 34:42.398
<font color="#00ffff">It's all right. I'll get it.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I'm so sorry, Jack.</font>

34:42.400 --> 34:43.838
<font color="#00ffff">It's all right.</font>

34:43.840 --> 34:46.598
<font color="#00ff00">She's trying to poison me.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Mum, I'm not.</font>

34:46.600 --> 34:50.000
<font color="#00ff00">She's trying to poison me. Help!</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Keep your voice down, Mum.</font>

34:53.440 --> 34:54.920
<font color="#00ff00">Frank.</font>

34:57.240 --> 35:00.240
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, Frank, where have you been?</font>

35:01.240 --> 35:03.760
<font color="#ffff00">Frank's, erm, my dad. </font><font color="#00ffff">Mm-hm.</font>

35:04.760 --> 35:06.598
<font color="#00ff00">I love you.</font>

35:06.600 --> 35:08.558
<font color="#00ff00">I love you so much, Frank.</font>

35:08.560 --> 35:11.958
<font color="#ffff00">I'm sorry, Mum.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I'm not sure you're his type.</font>

35:11.960 --> 35:13.640
<font color="#00ff00">Frank.</font>

35:14.640 --> 35:17.038
<font color="#00ffff">You know what they say,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">women are attracted to men</font>

35:17.040 --> 35:20.038
<font color="#00ffff">who look like their fathers. </font><font color="#ffff00">Good</font>
<font color="#ffff00">job I don't remember him, then.</font>

35:20.040 --> 35:21.758
<font color="#00ff00">She's trying to poison me.</font>

35:21.760 --> 35:24.278
<font color="#00ffff">No. No-one's trying to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">poison you, darling.</font>

35:24.280 --> 35:26.800
<font color="#00ffff">I promise you that. Look.</font>

35:29.520 --> 35:31.278
<font color="#00ffff">Delicious.</font>

35:31.280 --> 35:32.680
<font color="#00ffff">Try? Hm?</font>

35:33.680 --> 35:35.040
<font color="#00ff00">Oh.</font>

35:39.880 --> 35:41.400
<font color="#00ffff">Good stuff?</font>

35:55.400 --> 35:58.038
<font color="#ffffff">Can I help you? </font><font color="#00ffff">I'm Ann Carson.</font>

35:58.040 --> 36:00.280
<font color="#00ffff">I'm Derek Marshall's sister.</font>

36:01.280 --> 36:02.758
<font color="#ffffff">Oh.</font>

36:02.760 --> 36:04.758
<font color="#ffffff">I'm so sorry.</font>

36:04.760 --> 36:06.278
<font color="#00ffff">Erm...</font>

36:06.280 --> 36:11.880
<font color="#00ffff">..DI Raymond wanted some pictures</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of Derek for the appeal.</font>

36:14.840 --> 36:16.358
<font color="#00ffff">That's, erm...</font>

36:16.360 --> 36:20.038
<font color="#00ffff">That's his wife Sue</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and their daughter Hope.</font>

36:20.040 --> 36:23.280
<font color="#ffffff">You should probably take them</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to the police station.</font>

36:24.520 --> 36:27.040
<font color="#00ffff">I want to see my brother, please.</font>

36:40.760 --> 36:43.838
<font color="#ffffff">I strongly advise you</font>
<font color="#ffffff">against viewing his body.</font>

36:43.840 --> 36:46.518
<font color="#ffffff">I think it would be</font>
<font color="#ffffff">distressing for you.</font>

36:46.520 --> 36:48.760
<font color="#00ffff">But I'm allowed to, aren't I?</font>

36:49.760 --> 36:52.280
<font color="#00ffff">I can't...</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I can't move on unless I do.</font>

36:53.520 --> 36:56.400
<font color="#ffffff">His body would be unrecognisable,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I'm afraid.</font>

36:57.760 --> 37:00.320
<font color="#00ffff">So it's true</font>
<font color="#00ffff">what the police told me.</font>

37:04.520 --> 37:06.760
<font color="#00ffff">Dumping his body like garbage?</font>

37:08.520 --> 37:10.360
<font color="#00ffff">Like no-one loved him.</font>

37:11.760 --> 37:14.560
<font color="#00ffff">You wouldn't even treat a dog</font>
<font color="#00ffff">like that, would you?</font>

37:21.040 --> 37:24.038
<font color="#ffffff">Perhaps we should give Mum</font>
<font color="#ffffff">a break from the treatment.</font>

37:24.040 --> 37:26.038
<font color="#ffffff">Give her system a chance to recover.</font>

37:26.040 --> 37:29.038
<font color="#ffff00">I worry a delay will hinder</font>
<font color="#ffff00">her progress.</font>

37:29.040 --> 37:33.038
<font color="#ffffff">If her system is too weakened,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">there won't be any progress.</font>

37:33.040 --> 37:36.520
<font color="#ffffff">We need to be very careful with</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the way we administer her care.</font>

37:41.040 --> 37:42.918
<font color="#00ff00">What have you done, Frank?</font>

37:42.920 --> 37:44.518
<font color="#00ff00">What have you done?</font>

37:44.520 --> 37:46.838
<font color="#00ff00">You can't leave the baby alone.</font>

37:46.840 --> 37:49.518
<font color="#00ff00">You can't do that.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">You can't leave her alone.</font>

37:49.520 --> 37:51.518
<font color="#00ff00">Not for five minutes. </font><font color="#ffff00">Mum.</font>

37:51.520 --> 37:53.638
<font color="#00ff00">Go on, go!</font>

37:53.640 --> 37:57.238
<font color="#00ff00">I will never leave, Clarissa.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">She needs me more than you do.</font>

37:57.240 --> 38:00.518
<font color="#00ff00">I will never leave my baby alone.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Not ever.</font>

38:00.520 --> 38:02.680
<font color="#ffff00">Mum, it's OK.</font>

38:09.680 --> 38:11.120
<font color="#ffff00">Really?</font>

38:13.520 --> 38:16.318
<font color="#00ffff">I know your mum's confused</font>
<font color="#00ffff">about what's going on</font>

38:16.320 --> 38:19.318
<font color="#00ffff">but she clearly remembers</font>
<font color="#00ffff">how much she loves you.</font>

38:19.320 --> 38:23.520
<font color="#ffff00">All this grown-up stuff, Jack.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">It's not very us, is it?</font>

38:24.520 --> 38:27.198
<font color="#ffff00">I'm fine. </font><font color="#00ffff">Are you?</font>

38:27.200 --> 38:31.000
<font color="#ffff00">I always wondered</font>
<font color="#ffff00">if Dad left because of me.</font>

38:32.680 --> 38:34.520
<font color="#ffff00">And now I know.</font>

38:39.320 --> 38:42.678
<font color="#ffffff">None of our current evidence links</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Sue to the disposal of Derek's body</font>

38:42.680 --> 38:46.038
<font color="#ffffff">so it's difficult territory for</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the CPS to make formal charges.</font>

38:46.040 --> 38:49.198
<font color="#00ff00">But I only get to keep her in</font>
<font color="#00ff00">custody for 36 hours without charge</font>

38:49.200 --> 38:51.600
<font color="#00ff00">and then I'll have to let her go.</font>

38:53.040 --> 38:56.118
<font color="#ffffff">It would have taken some strength</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to haul a dead weight</font>

38:56.120 --> 38:58.518
<font color="#ffffff">of Derek's size</font>
<font color="#ffffff">into the pillar mould.</font>

38:58.520 --> 39:02.040
<font color="#ffffff">If she did do it, she certainly</font>
<font color="#ffffff">didn't do it alone.</font>

39:03.440 --> 39:04.920
<font color="#00ffff">Thank you.</font>

39:14.960 --> 39:16.400
<font color="#ffff00">Let's go.</font>

39:29.280 --> 39:30.678
<font color="#00ff00">DI Raymond.</font>

39:30.680 --> 39:34.038
<font color="#ffff00">I've followed the digital trail</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of Derek's money.</font>

39:34.040 --> 39:36.998
<font color="#ffff00">His payments moved through</font>
<font color="#ffff00">two Swiss bank accounts,</font>

39:37.000 --> 39:39.758
<font color="#ffff00">leading right back to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">our own back yard.</font>

39:39.760 --> 39:44.038
<font color="#ffff00">Derek Marshall was making payments</font>
<font color="#ffff00">shortly before he died</font>

39:44.040 --> 39:46.278
<font color="#ffff00">to Protech Visions.</font>

39:46.280 --> 39:51.758
<font color="#ffff00">It's a research facility</font>
<font color="#ffff00">headed up by a Dr Adam Brooklyn.</font>

39:51.760 --> 39:55.758
<font color="#ffff00">Payments that Sue continued with</font>
<font color="#ffff00">ever since.</font>

39:55.760 --> 39:58.878
<font color="#00ff00">Well, that explains where</font>
<font color="#00ff00">some of the money went.</font>

39:58.880 --> 40:01.758
<font color="#ffff00">Evidently.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">It's an expensive business.</font>

40:01.760 --> 40:06.958
<font color="#ffff00">It seems they specialise</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in reproductive biomedicine.</font>

40:06.960 --> 40:09.678
<font color="#00ff00">Fertility? </font><font color="#ffff00">Correct.</font>

40:09.680 --> 40:11.518
<font color="#00ff00">I'm no good at science.</font>

40:11.520 --> 40:15.120
<font color="#00ff00">What do you say you come along</font>
<font color="#00ff00">as my scientific interpreter?</font>

40:17.920 --> 40:20.360
<font color="#ffff00">Go on. You're on.</font>

40:31.280 --> 40:34.118
<font color="#ffffff">In essence,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">we're a storage facility.</font>

40:34.120 --> 40:37.758
<font color="#ffffff">We freeze eggs and sperm here</font>
<font color="#ffffff">for fertility</font>

40:37.760 --> 40:42.518
<font color="#ffffff">and boast the largest</font>
<font color="#ffffff">frozen tissue bank in Europe.</font>

40:42.520 --> 40:44.518
<font color="#ffff00">What are you researching?</font>

40:44.520 --> 40:47.038
<font color="#ffffff">We're exploring</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the practical applications</font>

40:47.040 --> 40:50.718
<font color="#ffffff">of sub-zero temperatures</font>
<font color="#ffffff">in medicine and surgery.</font>

40:50.720 --> 40:53.040
<font color="#ffffff">It's truly fascinating work.</font>

40:55.520 --> 40:58.040
<font color="#00ff00">Do you know</font>
<font color="#00ff00">a Sue or Derek Marshall?</font>

40:59.040 --> 41:01.918
<font color="#ffffff">I'm afraid that would be breaking</font>
<font color="#ffffff">client confidentiality.</font>

41:01.920 --> 41:04.038
<font color="#00ff00">I'm investigating</font>
<font color="#00ff00">a suspicious death.</font>

41:04.040 --> 41:06.680
<font color="#00ff00">I'm very happy to obtain</font>
<font color="#00ff00">a warrant, if you prefer.</font>

41:08.040 --> 41:10.678
<font color="#ffffff">Sue was one of our benefactors.</font>

